{"id": "1337425402603241473", "channel_id": "1337420357040345122", "type": 0, "author_id": "754158143419973683", "author_name": "yukine7473", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果照貓咪公告的說，應該現在從遊戲程式碼改比例就好，但就是玩家要吃運氣了\n做一個選擇系統需要人力跟時間", "timestamp": "2025-02-07T14:11:04.143000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🫠", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1337420357040345122", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "玩家只需要給錢好了，官方要考慮的就多了", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
